 Pocketbook edItor v 1.0.0
 to call menu press long OK or long click
 last versions you can find at http://fedorchenko.net/pi.php
 
 Command line options:
 -l n  - go to line n after file open
 -f name - open file name (if not set treat last argument as file name)
 -s select mode (for bogomil) write filename and selected line number to stderr at exit 
 (also exit at edit)

